reviewText: Of course, The Rift is not at all profound. Or anything near sophisticated. Some may see this series as trash; well; it is trashy, but it's funny trashy. And unique and surprising. Even the CGI effects are surprisingly well-done. Just enjoy. Like. very well-designed, well-executed trash.(Oh, this review relates to The Rift's Second Season. There's a movie, too, and a few more seasons.I doubt there's every been a show like this on cable/satellite. Certainly not on broadcast TV. Are youan adolescent or a grown-up terminal adolescent? This funny, surprising well-done Sci-Fi spoof is for you.) If you've got a trashy sense of humor you'll give it five stars too.
Title: Tripping the Rift - Season Two
